Subject: Deltasucroenergia - Admin AD Sync not working for two users
Description:
Hello team,

We are facing an issue where two admins from the admin group synced with EPP still appear as Usertype: EPP and not an AD one, they are also unable to use the password on the AD to login. I will attach a print for you.

Best regards,
What_We_Know__c:
2 AD users are not syncing correctly and are not able to log in using the AD password.
Initial troubleshooting was performed by the partner with a negative outcome.
Next_Steps__c: SSH into the server and delete the users from the DB and try the sync again
Solution_Comment__c: removing the users from the DB solved the issue and brought the correct ones from the AD sync
